    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">King Ferdinand I to Miklós Oláh (Prague, 22 January 1549)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>Because Oláh has the letters that King Ferdinand I exchanged with the
                            Pasha of Buda as well as the ones about the complaints from Eger, he
                            wants to see them while he is in Vienna and let Oláh know how he wishes
                            him to proceed.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Ferdinandus etc. Reverendissime Devote Fidelis Dilecte!</p>
                <p>Quoniam Devotio Tua litteras et scripta illa, quae <persName>bassa
                        Budensis</persName><note type="critic">Gazi Kasim Pasha was Pasha of Buda
                        between 1548–1551 and 1557–1558. He was also Bey of Mohács for a few years,
                        then Bey of Pécs, Bey of Székesfehérvár, and Pasha of Timișoara and Bosnia.
                        See <hi rend="smallcap">Gévay</hi> 1841, 6, <hi rend="smallcap">Dávid</hi>
                        1995; and <hi rend="smallcap">Dávid</hi> 1996.</note> ad nos et vicissim nos
                    ad eum dedimus, adhuc penes se habet, nos vero <del corresp="scriba">illis ipsis
                        litteris si scriptis brevi opus habituri simus, illam</del> tum <del
                        corresp="scriba">praedictas</del><add corresp="scriba" type="corr">iam
                        dictas</add> litteras, tum etiam Agriensium querelas et gravamina prae
                    manibus <del corresp="scriba">esse</del><add corresp="scriba" type="corr"
                        >habere</add> pro <del corresp="scriba">futura</del><add corresp="scriba"
                        type="corr">ulteriori</add> ea de re <del corresp="scriba">tentatio</del> in
                    ipso <persName>bassa</persName> fienda tractaverit, valde <choice>
                        <orig>cupiamus</orig>
                        <supplied>cupimus</supplied>
                    </choice>, sicuti Devotioni litteris, cum <placeName>Viennae</placeName> adhuc
                    essemus, ostendimus, eidem adeo Dominationi litteris committimus et mandamus, ut
                    tam <del corresp="scriba">mandatas litteras et scripta</del>
                    <persName>bassae Budensis</persName> ad nos et nostra ad eum scripta et
                    litteras, quam etiam Agriensium querelas et gravamina <del corresp="scriba"
                        >Agriensis</del><add corresp="scriba" type="corr">praedicta</add> ad nos
                    quam primum perferri curet nostram in eo exsecutura voluntatem.</p>
                <p>Datum in arce nostra regia <placeName>Pragae</placeName> die 22.
                    Ianuarii 1549.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso">
                <head>Probably on the outer side:</head>
                <p>Reverendissimo devoto fideli nobis dilecto Nicolao episcopo Agriensi,
                    consiliario et per regnum nostrum Hungariae cancellario nostro.</p>
                
            </div>
        </body>
